briefdescription.para: Convenience function to create a prim at the given path, and any necessary parent prims, in the given layer.

detaileddescription.para: If a prim already exists at the given path it will be returned unmodified.
The new specs are created with SdfSpecifierOver and an empty type. primPath must be a valid prim path.

briefdescription.para: Convenience function to create a prim at the given path, and any necessary parent prims, in the given layer.

detaileddescription.para: If a prim already exists at the given path, do nothing and return true.
Any newly created specs have SdfSpecifierOver and an empty type. primPath must be a valid prim path. Return false and issue an error if we fail to author the required scene description.
